rows.label: bf04390150_0020
rows.name:
Hm? Oh, it's Nia. I heard from Yoshitsune
that you betrayed us[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: bf04390150_0050
rows.name:
Of all people, the business partners
had to be these guys[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: bf04390150_0060
rows.name:
That's quite a way to talk about us,
especially from a rookie like you[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: bf04390150_0070
rows.name:
It's fine, Benkei.
Not only Nia, but even Heaven's Holy Grail is here.

rows.label: bf04390150_0080
rows.name: Ah, truly the heavens must have blessed us that we-

rows.label: bf04390150_0110
rows.name:
Kill the traitor,
bring back the Holy Grail, okay, Sata?

rows.label: bf04390150_0120
rows.name: It's a pain, but that's the mission.

rows.label: bf04390150_0140
rows.name: Both Hikari and Nia are our important comrades.

rows.label: bf04390150_0145
rows.name: I won't let you have your way!
